---
title: Sticky Soy BBQ Chicken with Sesame Infused Slaw
description: Everyone wants to eat lighter in the summer and boy do we have a meal just for that! Sticky sweet honey, lemongrass and soy-marinated chicken legs get grilled and paired with a sesame-infused creamy slaw full of veggies! A sprinkling of cashews brings the extra crunch factor!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sticky-soy-bbq-chicken-f18ee11d.jpg
